              "type": "numbered",
              "sentences": [
                {
                  "id": 1,
                  "english": "How do you like your present campus life?",
                  "chinese": "你觉得你现在的校园生活怎么样？",
                  "audio": "audio/Unit1/Topic1/Part1/1.mp3"
                },
                {
                  "id": 2,
                  "english": "The campus covers an area of twenty square kilometers.",
                  "chinese": "校园占地20平方公里。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 3,
                  "english": "The beautiful scenery of the campus, with its green lawns and green threes, creates a peaceful and pleasant learning environment.",
                  "chinese": "大学校园美丽的景色，有绿色的草坪和树木，营造出宁静宜人的学习环境。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 4,
                  "english": "Mobile phones are becoming a new scene on campus.",
                  "chinese": "手机正在成为校园里的一道新的风景。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 5,
                  "english": "They lead a busy and colorful life on campus.",
                  "chinese": "他们过着忙碌而丰富多彩的校园生活。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 6,
                  "english": "Are you involved in any extra-curricular activities on campus?",
                  "chinese": "你在校园里参加过什么课外活动吗？",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 7,
                  "english": "Our campus is surrounded by green mountains and a clear river.",
                  "chinese": "我们校园四周青山绿水。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 8,
                  "english": "The artificial lake has a beautiful scenery. Let's take some photos there.",
                  "chinese": "这个人工湖风景优美。我们去那儿拍些照片吧。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 9,
                  "english": "Walk along this road to the end and you will find the clinic. You won't miss it.",
                  "chinese": "沿着这条路走到尽头，你会找到诊所。你肯定能找到的。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 10,
                  "english": "We need to work hard for a harmonious campus.",
                  "chinese": "我们需要为和谐校园而努力。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 11,
                  "english": "The college campus is not only a place for study, but also a stage for students to show their talents and develop their interests.",
                  "chinese": "大学校园不仅是学习的地方，也是学生展示才华和发展兴趣的舞台。",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": 12,
                  "english": "You can get what you need for your daily life in the campus supermarket.",
                  "chinese": "你可以在校园超市买到你日常生活所需用品。",
                  "audio": ""
                }
              ],
