              "type": "article",
              "content": {
                "english": "Our university campus is located in the suburbs, covering an area of over 100 hectares. It features modern teaching buildings, well-equipped laboratories, a large library, and various sports facilities. The campus environment is beautiful with green trees, colorful flowers, and a peaceful lake. Students can enjoy a comfortable and convenient life here with dormitories, canteens, supermarkets, and other facilities available on campus.",
                "chinese": "我们大学校园位于郊区，占地100多公顷。校园内有现代化的教学楼、设备齐全的实验室、大型图书馆和各种体育设施。校园环境优美，绿树成荫，鲜花盛开，还有一个宁静的湖泊。学生可以在这里享受舒适便捷的生活，宿舍、食堂、超市等设施一应俱全。",
