          "parts": [
            {
              "id": 1,
              "title": "有效学习方法",
              "type": "article",
              "content": {
                "english": "Learning English requires consistent practice and exposure to the language. It's important to set realistic goals and create a study plan that fits your schedule. Try to immerse yourself in English as much as possible by watching movies, listening to music, and reading books in English. Don't be afraid to make mistakes - they are an essential part of the learning process. Practice speaking with native speakers or language partners to improve your fluency and confidence.",
                "chinese": "学习英语需要持续的练习和语言接触。设定现实的目标并制定适合你时间表的学习计划很重要。尽量通过看英语电影、听英语音乐和阅读英语书籍来沉浸在英语环境中。不要害怕犯错 - 错误是学习过程中必不可少的一部分。与母语为英语的人或语言伙伴练习口语，以提高流利度和自信心。",
                "audio": "https://www.soundjay.com/misc/sounds/bell-ringing-05.wav"
              },
              "vocabulary": [
                {
                  "english": "Consistent",
                  "chinese": "持续的",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
                  "english": "Immerse",
                  "chinese": "沉浸",
                  "audio": ""
                },
                {
